</script></p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">emerge fortune-mod <span class="c"># Gentoo, Funtoo, ...</span>
<span class="nb">sudo </span>apt <span class="nb">install </span>fortune <span class="c"># Debian, Ubuntu, Mint, ...</span>
<span class="nb">sudo </span>pacman <span class="nt">-S</span> fortune-mod <span class="c"># Arch, Manjaro,...</span>
<span class="nb">sudo </span>yum <span class="nb">install </span>fortune <span class="c"># Red Hat, CentOS, ...</span>
<span class="nb">sudo </span>dnf <span class="nb">install </span>fortune <span class="c"># Fedora</span></code></pre></figure>

<p>On BSDs it is already installed by default! :)</p>

<h1 id="use">Use</h1>
<p>To generate a sentence just run the command:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">fortune</code></pre></figure>

<!-- LISTA MIN -->
