<h1 id="some-options">Some options:</h1>

<ul>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">fortune -a</code> - generates all sorts of sentences: long, short, offensive;</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">fortune -o</code> - only generates offensive phrases, for those who like! Observa√ß√£o (Note, in Gentoo and Funtoo, you need to compile with the flag <code class="highlighter-rouge">USE="offensive"</code> for offensives to appear);</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">fortune -l</code> - only long sentences;</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">fortune -c</code> - only short sentences;</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">fortune -m</code> - Only phrases that contain at least one word that matches the regex you pass; For more options use the manual: <code class="highlighter-rouge">man fortune</code></li>
</ul>

